Set Up Workforce Engagement

Before your teams can use Workforce Engagement, turn it on, assign permission sets, and create a custom Lightning Console app for your team to use.

1. Purchase the Workforce Engagement add-on.
2. From Setup, turn on Workforce Engagement and its features: 
   Enable Workforce Engagement
   Enable the Workforce Engagement Configuration App
   Enable adherence metrics
3. Assign all three Workforce Engagement permission sets to your own user profile and fellow users.
4. Create a custom Lightning Console app for Workforce Engagement:
   Add Agent Home, Historical Adherence, Intelligent Forecasts, etc.
5. If the Engagement Analytics App becomes out of date, update it as the Workforce Engagement administrator.
title: Setting up Salesforce Service Cloud Workforce Engagement
